---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Services — Recverse"
  description="AI MVPs, ERP-adjacent delivery, IT project management, and modern web presence for SMBs. Brainstorm → scope → proposal."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Services</div>
      <h1 class="h1">Your ideas → our brainstorm → my proposal</h1>
      <p class="p">
        The focus is pragmatic, deliverable outcomes — not slideware.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h2 class="h2">AI MVP / PoC</h2>
          <p class="p">Prioritize use cases, build an MVP, integrate cleanly — with pragmatic security and ops considerations.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:14px;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=AI%20MVP%20%2F%20PoC">Request</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h2 class="h2">ERP & IT project management</h2>
          <p class="p">Requirements and delivery planning, stakeholder alignment, interface/risk control. Strong focus on go-live readiness.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:14px;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=ERP%20%2F%20IT%20Project%20Management">Request</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="padding:18px;">
          <h2 class="h2">Modern web presence</h2>
          <p class="p">Fast, trustworthy, conversion-clear. Performance-first, clean structure, maintainable engineering.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:14px;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Web%20Presence%20%2F%20Redesign">Request</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:18px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Website Privacy Check</h2>
        <p class="p">
          A rapid review of your website’s privacy basics (cookies, forms, tracking, third-party services).
          Deliverable: concrete, prioritized to-dos.
        </p>
        <p class="p"><strong>Price:</strong> SMB CHF 380 · Individual CHF 100</p>
        <div style="margin-top:14px; display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Website%20Privacy%20Check&package=SMB">SMB inquiry</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Website%20Privacy%20Check&package=Individual">Individual inquiry</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="padding:18px; margin-top:18px;">
        <h2 class="h2">Business & process consulting</h2>
        <p class="p">
          We identify bottlenecks, make pragmatic decisions, and implement. Processes evolve — as does the business and its environment.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top:14px;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Business%20%26%20Process%20Consulting">Start a brainstorm</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
